<anchor id="power__mgr_8h_1power_mgr"/> <simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The tasks of the power manager base class are:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Controlling the metrics transmission interval using a timer</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Providing method to switch off UART</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Register and notify metrics providing tasks</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Reporting reset cause and boot counter</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Providing task function to derived classes</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>This source code is confidential and proprietary information of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. You may not disclose, copy, or distribute this source code or any part thereof without the explicit permission of AXO Track GmbH, Berlin. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
